Invoice generator - Play application
===================+++==============

This file will be packaged with your application when using `activator dist`.
Reactive microservice using mongo.

Controllers
===========

- InvoiceController.scala:

    POST    /invoice/:number/days/:days
    GET     /invoice/:number


Components
==========

- Module.scala:

  Shows how to use Guice to bind all the components needed by your application.

- Invoicer.scala:

  Will generate the invoice pdf for the number of days given.

Filters
=======

- Filters.scala:

  Creates the list of HTTP filters used by your application.
